communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[ProMED-mail awaits more information regarding this relatively large outbreak. In a potluck dinner where everyone brings a different dish, there will be lots of potential reservoirs to investigate. Home-canned foods should be high on the list. With a case attack rate of more than 30 per cent, a food diary could be useful in knowing which foods the affected individuals consumed. - Mod.LL

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3314627,237.]
